What is Google Feud?

In Google Feud, players are given the start of a Google search and must guess the top 10 most likely auto-complete answers. Points are awarded based on accuracy, with wrong guesses limiting your chances.

How to Play Google Feud?

  • Choose a category: Culture, People, Names, or Questions.
  • Try to guess the top auto-complete results for a partial Google search.
  • Earn points for correct answers and climb the score ladder.
  • Game ends after three wrong guesses per round.
